Origin and attribution
----------------------

This repository began as a fork of a MIT-licensed upstream writing project and
has since been renamed and substantially rebuilt as Novelist, a .NET 10 +
Photino.NET desktop app with a React/Vite frontend. The specific upstream
attribution is kept in README.

The active Novelist implementation lives under src/, frontend/src/, and tests/.
The retired Go/Wails product path is not part of the active implementation.
Active source paths, runtime files, and user-facing tool paths use the
Novelist name.

The upstream project later changed its license. Novelist does not merge
post-relicense upstream code and remains distributed under the MIT License for
the code in this repository.

The MIT copyright and permission notice in LICENSE must be preserved in copies
or substantial portions of this software.
